<HEADLINE>
<P>
NO NEW AGE GROUP, NO PARTICULAR CAUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In the Feb. 20 View section, there was an article entitled "Eyes on a Cosmic 
Prize" which contained misinformation about John-Roger, spiritual director of 
the Church of the Movement of Spiritual Inner Awareness. 
</P>
<P>
 John-Roger is not a "new age leader."Our church does not consider itself a 
"new age" church. The Church of the Movement of Spiritual Inner Awareness is an 
ecumenical church that presents a new look at ancient spiritual philosophies. 
</P>
<P>
 John-Roger does not have a "cause." He has a wide range of life experiences 
that many people find valuable as reference points for learning how to live a 
happy, joyful, peaceful life that is focused on sharing, loving and being of 
service. He does not have a foundation in Santa Monica. 
</P>
<P>
 JEENI WONG 
</P>
<P>
 Public Representative 
</P>
<P>
 Movement of Spiritual Inner Awareness-USA 
</P>
