</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Total album and single sales of CDs and cassettes for the week ended April 24, 
compared to week-ago and year-ago levels, in millions of units: 03,13,08,09 
Albums Singles Latest Week 9.3 1.7 Week ago 9.8 1.8 Year ago 8.7 1.9 Hits 
Magazine Tip of the Week 
</P>
<P>
 Amid an overwhelming amount of Madonna bashing -- even by her standards -- the 
Material Girl has a smash single on her hands. "I'll Remember," from the 
Maverick-Warner Bros. soundtrack to the new film "With Honors," is scoring huge 
requests at radio stations across the country, with programmers reporting broad 
demographic appeal. MTV is also reporting numerous requests for the video. Most 
significantly, single sales are exploding and have placed the new scourge of 
late-night TV firmly in the Top 10. 
