<HEADLINE>
<P>
PACIFICA BEATS RANCHO ALAMITOS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Toni Mascarenas pitched a two-hitter with five strikeouts as seventh-ranked 
Pacifica beat host Rancho Alamitos, 1-0, Thursday in a Garden Grove League 
softball game. 
</P>
<P>
 It was the sixth shutout for Mascarenas. 
</P>
<P>
 Autumn Gwinner singled, stole second and third, and scored on a throwing error 
for Pacifica (14-5-1, 8-1-1).  
</P>
<P>
 Julie Littman had two singles for Rancho Alamitos (10-6, 5-5). 
</P>
</TEXT>
