 The Hollywood Historic Trust is accepting nominations through May 31 for the 
Hollywood Walk of Fame.Nominations will be accepted in five categories -- 
motion pictures, television, radio, recording and live theater. 
</P>
<P>
 The Walk of Fame Committee will select about 12-15 names for inclusion on the 
