Noon," KCAL. 
</P>
<P>
 * News special: "Firefight," KCET; "The Real Debate -- L.A. Mayoral Debate," 
KCOP. 
</P>
<P>
 * Live coverage of an unscheduled news event: "Fire Coverage," KTTV; "Laguna 
Fire," KABC; "Malibu Fire Coverage," KTLA; "Malibu-Topanga Fire," KCBS; 
"Southland on Fire," KCAL. 
</P>
<P>
 * Informational/public-affairs series (remote): "City View," KABC; "Life & 
Times," KCET. 
</P>
<P>
 * Informational/public-affairs series (studio-based): "Life & Times (studio 
edition)," KCET; "Making It! Minority Success Stories," KTLA; "Newsmakers," 
KCBS; "Southland Today," KDOC; "Troubleshooter Judd McIlvain," KCBS. 
</P>
<P>
 * Children/youth series: "Kidquiz," KCBS; "Storytime," KCET. 
</P>
<P>
 * Live special events: "Live From the Hollywood Bowl," KCOP; "Together: 
Neighbor to Neighbor -- A Town Hall Gathering," KABC; "The 1993 Tournament of 
Roses Parade," KTLA; "1993 Tournament of Roses Parade," KTTV. 
</P>
<P>
 * News commentary: Bill Press, KCOP; Dennis Farrier, KCAL; John Corcoran, 
KCAL; Michael Tuck, KCBS; Hal Fishman, KTLA. 
</P>
<P>
