Kerman Maddox, "Life & Times," KCET; Vin Scully, "Los Angeles Dodgers 
Pre-Game," KTLA; Larry McCormick, Michelle Ruiz, "Making It! Minority Success 
Stories," KTLA; Marabina Jaimes, Mark Ritts, "Storytime," KCET; Judd McIlvain, 
"Troubleshooter Judd McIlvain," KCBS. 
